Class ClosedShape

  • java.lang.Object
    • ClosedShape

  • public class ClosedShape
extends java.lang.Object
    A ClosedShape is any shape that can be drawn without taking a pencil off a piece of paper. It's representation on computer has a line colour and a position on the drawable screen component. It can be filled in with colour or opaque. This class is a super class for all shapes.
